  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <lg xml:id="TolC082">
          <l>kaṇkāl puṟamakam uḷḷuḻai kīḻmēl</l>
	<l>piṉcār ayalpuṭai tēvakai yeṉāa</l>
	<l>muṉṉiṭai kaṭaitalai valamiṭa meṉāa</l>
	<l>aṉṉa piṟavum ataṉpāla eṉmaṉār.</l>
        </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/62/mode/1up">65</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/64/mode/1up">66</ref>.</p>
      <p>ic cūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, muṟaiyāṉē ēḻām vēṟṟumai yuṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
      <p>urai: ēḻām eṇṇu muṟaimaikkaṇṇatu kaṇ eṉṉum peyaraiyuṭaiya vēṟṟumaic col, viṉaicey yiṭamum nilamum kālamum eṉpaṉa mūṉṟu poruṭkaṇṇum varum atu eṉṟavāṟu</p>
      <p>viṉai ceyyiṭam:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC082-Ilam-cit1">
	    <l>'taṭṭuppuṭaikkaṇ vantāṉ'</l>
      </lg> 
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>nilam:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC082-Ilam-cit2">
	    <l>'māṭattukkaṇ iruntāṉ'</l>
      </lg> 
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>kālam:</p>
	    <lg xml:id="TolC082-Ilam-cit3"> 
      <l>'māriyuḷ vantāṉ'</l>
      </lg> 
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>iṉi, av vēṟṟumaiyurupu palavākaliṉ. avaṟṟai virik kiṉṟār.</p>
      <p>avai varumāṟu:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC082-Ilam-cit4">
      <l>ūrkkaṇṇiruntāṉ,</l>
      </lg> 
      <lg xml:id="TolC082-Ilam-cit5"></lg>
      <l>ūrkkāliruntāṉ,</l> 
      <lg xml:id="TolC082-Ilam-cit6"></lg>
      <l>ūrppuṟat tiruntāṉ,</l> 
      <lg xml:id="TolC082-Ilam-cit7"></lg>
      <l>ūrakattiruntāṉ,</l> 
      <lg xml:id="TolC082-Ilam-cit8"></lg>
      <l>ūruḷiruntāṉ,</l> 
      <lg xml:id="TolC082-Ilam-cit9"></lg>
      <l>cāṉṟōruḻaic ceṉṟāṉ,</l>
      <lg xml:id="TolC082-Ilam-cit10"></lg>
      <l>māṭattiṉ kīḻiruntāṉ,</l> 
      <lg xml:id="TolC082-Ilam-cit11"></lg>
      <l>māṭattiṉ mēliruntāṉ,</l> 
      <lg xml:id="TolC082-Ilam-cit12"></lg>
      <l>ērppiṉ ceṉṟāṉ,</l> 
      <lg xml:id="TolC082-Ilam-cit13"></lg>
      <l>'kāṭṭuccā rōṭum',</l> 
      <lg xml:id="TolC082-Ilam-cit14"></lg>
      <l>ūraya liruntāṉ,</l> 
      <lg xml:id="TolC082-Ilam-cit15"></lg>
      <l>ūrppuṭai yiruntāṉ.</l>
      <p>tēvakai eṉpatu ticaikkūṟṟu: atu,</p> 
      <lg xml:id="TolC082-Ilam-cit16"></lg>
      <l>'vaṭakkaṇ vēṅkaṭam, teṟkaṇ kumari'</l> 
      <p>eṉa varum.</p>
      <p>eṉāa eṉpatu iṭaiccol.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC082-Ilam-cit17"></lg>
      <l>tērmuṉ ceṉṟāṉ,</l> 
      <lg xml:id="TolC082-Ilam-cit18"></lg>
      <l>cāṉṟōriṭaiyiruntāṉ,</l> 
      <lg xml:id="TolC082-Ilam-cit19"></lg>
      <l>kōyiṟ kaṭaic ceṉṟāṉ,</l> 
      <lg xml:id="TolC082-Ilam-cit20"></lg>
      <l>tantaitalaic ceṉṟāṉ,</l> 
      <lg xml:id="TolC082-Ilam-cit21"></lg>
      <l>kaivalattuḷḷatu koṭukkum,</l> 
      <lg xml:id="TolC082-Ilam-cit22"></lg>
      <l>kaiyiṭattiruntāṉ</l> 
      <p>eṉavum varum.</p>
      <p>'aṉṉa piṟavum' eṉṟataṉāl 'kiḻavō ṭēttu' eṉṉun toṭakkattaṉa koḷka.	(15)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n87/mode/1up">84</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n89/mode/1up">86</ref>.</p>
      <p>i - ḷ. kaṇ mutalāka iṭamīṟākac collappaṭṭa pattoṉpatuporuḷum avaipōlvaṉa piṟavum ēḻāvataṉ ṟiṟattaṉa. e-ṟu.</p>
<p>kaṇṇeṉṉum poruḷāvatu <lg xml:id="TolC082-Cena-cit1"><l>'kaṇṇiṉṟu kūṟutalāṟṟāṉavaṉāyiṉ.'</l></lg> e-m. <lg xml:id="TolC082-Cena-cit2"><l>'kaṇṇakaṉñālam.'</l></lg> e-m. kaṇṇeṉṉumiṭaiccollāṉuṇarttappaṭum iṭapporuṇmai. tēvakaiyeṉpatu ticaikkūṟu. kaṇkālpuṟamakamuḷḷeṉpaṉa mutalāyiṉavaṟṟatu poruḷvēṟṟumai vaḻakku nōkki yuṇarntukoḷka.</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC082-Cena-cit3"><l>kaṇṇiṉṟu colliyāṉai eṉkaṇṇiṉṟivaicollaṟpālaiyallai</l></lg>
<p>eṉṟum,</p> 
<lg xml:id="TolC082-Cena-cit4"><l>ūrkkāṟceyyai ūrkkaṭcey</l></lg>
<p>eṉṟum,</p> 
<lg xml:id="TolC082-Cena-cit5"><l>ūrppuṟattu niṉṟa marattai ūrkkaṇmaram</l></lg>
<p>eṉṟum,</p> 
<lg xml:id="TolC082-Cena-cit6"><l>eyilakattup pukkāṉai eyiṟkaṭpukkāṉ</l></lg>
<p>eṉṟum,</p> 
<lg xml:id="TolC082-Cena-cit7"><l>illuḷiruntāṉai iṟkaṇiruntāṉ</l></lg> 
<p>eṉṟum,</p> 
<lg xml:id="TolC082-Cena-cit8"><l>aracaṉuḻaiyiruntāṉai aracaṉkaṇiruntāṉ</l></lg> 
<p>eṉṟum,</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC082-Cena-cit9"><l>āliṉkīḻkkiṭantavāvai āliṉkaṭkiṭantatu</l></lg> 
<p>eṉṟum,</p> 
<lg xml:id="TolC082-Cena-cit10"><l>marattiṉmēlirunta kuraṅkai marattiṉkaṇiruntatu</l></lg> 
<p>eṉṟum,</p> 
<lg xml:id="TolC082-Cena-cit11"><l>ērppiṉceṉṟāṉai ērkkaṭceṉṟāṉ</l></lg>
<p>eṉṟum,</p> 
<lg xml:id="TolC082-Cena-cit12"><l>kāṭṭuccārōṭuvataṉaik kāṭṭiṉkaṇōṭum</l></lg> 
<p>eṉṟum,</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC082-Cena-cit13"><l>uṟaiyūrkkayaṉiṉṟa cirāppaḷḷikkuṉṟai uṟaiyūrkkaṭkuṉṟu</l></lg>
<p>eṉṟum,</p> 
<lg xml:id="TolC082-Cena-cit14"><l>eyiṟpuṭainiṉṟārai eyiṟkaṇiṉṟār</l></lg> 
<p>eṉṟum,</p> 
<lg xml:id="TolC082-Cena-cit15"><l>vaṭapālvēṅkaṭam teṉpāṟkumari eṉpaṉavaṟṟai vaṭakkaṇvēṅkaṭam teṟkaṭkumari</l></lg> 
<p>eṉṟum,</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC082-Cena-cit16"><l>pulimuṉpaṭṭāṉaip pulikkaṭpaṭṭāṉ</l></lg> 
<p>eṉṟum,</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC082-Cena-cit17"><l>nūliṉiṭaiyuṅkaṭaiyuntalaiyuniṉṟa maṅkalattai nūṟkaṇmaṅkalam</l></lg>
<p>eṉṟum,</p> 
<lg xml:id="TolC082-Cena-cit18"><l>kaivalattuḷḷataṉaik kaikkaṇuḷḷatu</l></lg>
<p>eṉṟum,</p> 
<lg xml:id="TolC082-Cena-cit19"><l>taṉṉiṭattu nikaḻvataṉait taṉkaṇikaḻvatu</l></lg> 
<p>eṉṟum, av viṭapporuḷpaṟṟi ēḻāmvēṟṟumai vantavāṟu kaṇṭu koḷka.</p>
<p>eṉāaveṉpatu eṇṇiṭaiccol.</p>
<p>kaṇ mutalāyiṉavellām urupeṉṟārāl uraiyāciriyareṉiṉ;-urupāyiṉ, ēḻāvataṟkuk kaṇṇeṉpatu urupātal mēlē peṟappaṭṭamaiyāṟ peyarttuṅ kaṇkāleṉṟal kūṟiyatu kūṟiṟṟāmākalāṉum, ūrppuṟattiruntāṉ, ūrakattiruntāṉ, kaivalattuḷḷatu koṭukkum eṉap puṟam akam valameṉpaṉavaṟṟuvaḻi attuccāriyai koṭuttutāraṇaṅkāṭṭiṉamaiyāṉum, avarkkatu karuttaṉṟeṉka. urupallavēl, eṉṉuḻai, eṉmuṉ eṉa nilaimoḻi urupiṟkōtiya ceykai peṟṟavāṟeṉṉaiyeṉiṉ:-  'ataṟporuṭṭākaliṉ' eṉavum 'tammuṭaiya taṇṇaḷiyun tāmum' eṉavum urupiṉporuḷpaṭa varum piṟamoḻi vantuḻiyum nilaimoḻi acceykai peṟṟu niṟṟaliṉ; acceykai urupupuṇarccikkēyeṉṉum yāppuṟaviṉṟeṉka.</p>
<p>aṉṉapiṟavumeṉṟataṉāl, poruṭkaṇuṇarvu, eṉkaṇaṉpuṭaiyaṉ, malarkkaṇāṟṟam, ākāyattukkaṭparuntu eṉṉuntoṭakkattaṉa koḷka.	(21)</p>
    </body>
  </text>
